// // ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// //  ARCHITECTURE
// //  Chat shape: { id, title, messages[], createdAt, updatedAt,
// //                jobMode: bool, jobProfile: JobProfile | null,
// //                docs: DocMeta[] }
// //  DocMeta: { id, name, chunks, size, isPdf, addedAt }
// //  RAW TEXT is stored in module-level ragTextStore Map (NOT localStorage)
// //  — avoids the 5MB localStorage limit that was silently killing uploads
// //  — re-indexed from ragTextStore whenever chat switches
// //  RAG FIXES:
// //    1. Stale closure on re-index effect → now depends on [cid, chats]
// //    2. rawText no longer stored in localStorage → ragTextStore Map
// //    3. chunkText improved for PDF text (handles \n, broken whitespace)
// //    4. Upload immediately indexes + triggers re-index
// //    5. docCount checked correctly after upload
// // ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

